duties_responsibilities.duty: Accurately loading and unloading trailers, verifying route load(s), and maintaining the shipping yard.
Counting and checking products for accuracy and quality, maintaining accurate records, reporting overages and shortages, and participating in "Cycle Counts".
Operating material handling equipment, including pallet jack, forklift, troubleshoot packing equipment, label machines, tapers, palletizers, etc.

education_certification.credential: At least 18 years of age or older.
